==Arabic alphabet==

===Letter===
'''{{ARchar|ر / ‍ر}}''' (rā’)

# The tenth letter of the [[Arabic]] alphabet. It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ذ]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[ز]]}}.
# The twentieth letter in traditional [[abjad]] order, which is used in place of numerals for list numbering ([[abjad numerals]]). It is preceded by {{ARchar|[[ق]]}} and followed by {{ARchar|[[ش]]}}.

